name: MEME TAO
description: MEME TAO is a meme coin-centric discovery and management platform designed to bring order to the memecoin space. It's built around a DAO and aims to be a perfect tool to find and acquire tokens that exhibit potential. In order to incentivize and assist newbies to the market, in both charting a smarter course and not getting rug-pulled, MEME TAO tokenizes the patterns and choices of experienced memecoin market veterans.
